usage: uw ecflow server [-h] [--version] [--insecure] [--port PORT] [--report]
                        [--quiet] [--verbose]

Start an ecFlow server

Optional arguments:
  -h, --help
      Show help and exit
  --version
      Show version info and exit
  --insecure
      Start server without SSL security
  --port PORT
      TCP port for the ecFlow server (default: random from 49152-65535)
  --report
      Output server details (hostname, port) as JSON to stdout
  --quiet, -q
      Print no logging messages
  --verbose, -v
      Print all logging messages
